        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 8:29",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 28:2",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; so Kimchi; or rather, according to Arama, unto the holy name of God, to whom prayer is to be directed; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and bless the Lord; which is repeated, to show the importance of the work, that it might not be forgotten and neglected; this being a principal part of spiritual service, and greatly acceptable to God. ",
